column2: "Um... I was wondering if you knew a way to get by without fighting any enemies?"
"Well, quitting ARKS is definitely one option but I really suck at life so..."
"I kind of want to get by as an ARKS so I don't have to look for a new job"
"I mean, I really can't do anything at all, so pretending to work in ARKS is my best bet I think."
"But uh, anyways sorry for wasting your time again. Bye."
